<h1>Play it my way!</h1>

<br/>Offering personalized playback of amazon/amazon prime/youtube videos, and more!  
<br/>We believe you have the right to watch shows the way you'd like to in the privacy of your home, and we're here to help you get there.  See our <a href=/faq>FAQ</a> for details. 
<br/>Ever wished you could mute profanities or skip scenes that distract during movies? We are a community that works together to make that possible.  We hope to give you control over what is played in your home.
<br/>Play it my way is free!
<br/>
<h2>How it works:</h2>
Play it my way works by monitoring your video as it plays back your legally streamed movies online (ex: amazon using your own account/purchases, youtube, etc.).  When it detects you're in a part your would prefer to not see, or not hear, it jumps over those scenes or mutes them for you.
<br>Currently it works as a browser plugin, so you can watch edited on your computer, or on your TV if you hook your computer/laptop to your TV.  You could for instance run a long (<a href='https://smile.amazon.com/BlueRigger-Speed-Ethernet-Supports-Return/dp/B003XM73P2'>25'</a> or <a href='https://smile.amazon.com/BlueRigger-Wall-High-Speed-Cable/dp/B004GW25WY?sa-no-redirect=1'>50'</a>) HDMI cable from your computer to your TV.

